WEBVTT

02:07.880 --> 02:09.280
What are you doing?

02:22.720 --> 02:24.040
Wash your hands.

02:25.360 --> 02:26.480
I won't.

02:28.160 --> 02:30.160
They'll just get dirty again anyway.

03:42.200 --> 03:43.200
Ji Ling…

03:57.560 --> 04:00.880
You're Ji Ling, aren't you?

04:03.280 --> 04:05.040
I've already answered that.

04:06.560 --> 04:08.760
I saw you eat him with my own eyes.

04:08.840 --> 04:10.400
You demons eat people.

04:10.480 --> 04:14.200
Don't pin what you did on me.

04:14.280 --> 04:15.880
You ate his memories.

04:26.920 --> 04:28.960
You have Ji Ling's memories, don't you?

04:32.760 --> 04:33.600
Ji Ling

04:33.680 --> 04:36.880
is just a puppet I made with sacred power.

04:36.960 --> 04:38.600
He wears my face

04:38.680 --> 04:41.520
to roam the human world
and carry out tasks.

04:43.040 --> 04:44.680
What memories could he have?

04:53.360 --> 04:56.080
Then why didn't you throw me
in the dungeon here?

04:57.160 --> 05:00.000
Why treat me so well
and put up with my nonsense?

05:02.000 --> 05:04.120
Only Ji Ling would pamper me like this.

05:05.040 --> 05:08.120
He'd do everything to please me.

05:08.720 --> 05:10.440
I can treat you badly too.

05:11.560 --> 05:13.000
Want a taste?

05:15.920 --> 05:17.240
The other day, you said

05:18.040 --> 05:20.120
Ji Ling was your youth, your past.

05:21.040 --> 05:23.320
You're the piece of my youth, my past

05:23.400 --> 05:24.720
I most wanted to keep.

05:27.000 --> 05:28.120
What did that

05:29.640 --> 05:31.240
really mean?

05:32.880 --> 05:35.520
Ji Ling's innocence is rare in this world.

05:37.680 --> 05:39.240
Everyone wants to keep it.

05:40.520 --> 05:41.920
You do too, don't you?

05:45.160 --> 05:47.800
You sure love to beat around the bush.

05:49.600 --> 05:50.960
Then let me ask another way.

05:53.880 --> 05:55.040
You haven't learned?

05:57.760 --> 05:59.480
Want to get hit by backlash again?

06:01.800 --> 06:03.400
Who said I'd use Word Magic?

06:04.840 --> 06:06.920
Ji Ling taught me this.

06:08.000 --> 06:10.160
One last time.

06:10.680 --> 06:11.800
Are you

06:13.120 --> 06:14.280
Ji Ling or not?

06:16.560 --> 06:19.480
<i>Miss Lu, I'll ask again.</i>

06:20.120 --> 06:21.480
Have we met before?

06:31.400 --> 06:32.280
No.

06:35.400 --> 06:36.840
Hear that?

07:23.600 --> 07:25.080
They're already here.

07:25.160 --> 07:26.720
We should head out too.

07:27.600 --> 07:29.400
For the next piece
of Dragon Deity's Power?

07:32.360 --> 07:33.600
But…

07:35.240 --> 07:37.200
I haven't retrieved
Wu Shiguang's prayer beads yet.

07:39.840 --> 07:42.440
The Twelve Thoughts
must be given willingly.

07:42.960 --> 07:44.240
They were never easy to take.

07:45.080 --> 07:46.680
Don't blame yourself.

07:46.760 --> 07:49.760
I've sent someone else to handle it.

07:51.320 --> 07:54.240
Let's go. To the Ruined Sand.

08:15.640 --> 08:17.480
Okay. I'll go get a new puppet.

08:18.080 --> 08:19.120
No need.

08:27.200 --> 08:31.360
This time, I'll go with you myself.

08:33.280 --> 08:35.000
Master, why risk it?

08:36.280 --> 08:38.039
Just make another Ji Ling.

08:39.880 --> 08:41.640
I'll go with him again.

08:42.159 --> 08:43.320
And upon our return,

08:43.400 --> 08:45.400
we'll share all the memories with you.

08:46.480 --> 08:47.320
Isn't that the same?

08:48.960 --> 08:50.480
I can't hide in the sect anymore.

08:51.640 --> 08:53.920
The Oracle Stone's given the prophecy.

08:54.960 --> 08:56.800
I don't have much time left.

08:58.800 --> 09:00.560
I have to face this myself.

09:55.160 --> 09:56.960
You shouldn't be here.

10:17.680 --> 10:18.840
What are you doing here?

10:20.520 --> 10:23.880
I heard you've lived in seclusion

10:24.480 --> 10:25.880
all these years,

10:26.400 --> 10:27.240
acting strange.

10:27.920 --> 10:29.640
That you've stayed
in the underground Scale Cave,

10:30.160 --> 10:33.280
sucking the life force from mortals
to heal yourself.

10:34.120 --> 10:35.480
So I came to see

10:37.080 --> 10:39.000
if innocent people

10:39.680 --> 10:41.000
are really locked up here,

10:42.000 --> 10:43.480
used as medicine.

10:44.400 --> 10:45.920
The world's gossip,

10:46.800 --> 10:48.080
truth or lies,

10:48.160 --> 10:49.920
can you really keep track?

10:50.960 --> 10:54.640
The gravely ill often bathe in incense

10:55.160 --> 10:56.440
and wear flowers

10:57.080 --> 10:59.600
to hide the smell of decay and death.

11:00.200 --> 11:04.480
Master, you're heavy with fragrance.

11:05.360 --> 11:07.000
What are you trying to hide?

11:07.080 --> 11:09.720
The Dragon Deity
has a pure celestial aura.

11:09.800 --> 11:11.840
What fragrance? How dare you!

11:29.680 --> 11:32.080
You don't want to be trapped here forever,

11:33.120 --> 11:34.320
do you?

11:35.800 --> 11:38.000
You'll let me return?

11:38.680 --> 11:39.640
I will.

11:40.480 --> 11:42.600
But first, come with me somewhere.

12:11.200 --> 12:13.480
Where I lived as a child is nearby.

12:17.040 --> 12:18.080
These blocks look like rocks,

12:20.280 --> 12:21.600
but they're actually from a tree.

12:23.880 --> 12:24.760
A tree?

12:25.880 --> 12:27.120
My father told me

12:28.480 --> 12:29.680
this place once grew

12:30.400 --> 12:33.040
a giant ancient tree.

12:34.480 --> 12:38.800
Then, lightning struck and shattered it.

12:39.760 --> 12:41.240
Its branches split apart,

12:41.840 --> 12:44.240
and the trunk grew wild,

12:44.320 --> 12:46.120
ending up like this.

12:47.800 --> 12:49.120
I know this tree.

12:52.200 --> 12:56.200
It has a name, The Crying Elm.

12:57.600 --> 12:58.440
The Crying Elm?

13:00.040 --> 13:01.760
Goddess Nuwa once said

13:01.840 --> 13:04.560
the Crying Elm was a sacred ancient tree,

13:04.640 --> 13:07.080
lush and sheltering all life.

13:12.640 --> 13:14.400
I never knew

13:14.480 --> 13:17.400
this is all that's left,
broken, decaying roots.

13:18.200 --> 13:19.360
When I was little,

13:19.440 --> 13:21.360
I used to sneak here to play.

13:22.920 --> 13:26.520
My master also told me
about the murals here.

13:27.800 --> 13:30.040
An ancient tribe called Aodeng

13:30.560 --> 13:32.520
settled near these roots.

13:34.400 --> 13:36.120
But soon after,

13:36.200 --> 13:37.280
they all fell gravely ill.

13:38.000 --> 13:39.320
Many died.

13:50.160 --> 13:53.880
So, they prayed to the heavens.

13:54.680 --> 13:55.920
To their surprise,

13:56.440 --> 13:58.280
a star actually fell from the sky.

13:58.920 --> 14:01.920
It crashed in flames,
sparking a heavenly fire.

14:17.240 --> 14:18.680
When the fire died down,

14:19.480 --> 14:23.040
they found in the pit a celestial stone.

14:23.760 --> 14:25.720
They called it the Star Stone.

14:26.320 --> 14:27.520
Even more miraculous,

14:28.760 --> 14:31.200
the plague that had haunted them

14:31.280 --> 14:32.960
vanished without medicine.

14:33.880 --> 14:37.000
So the Aodeng people
revered the Star Stone as sacred.

14:39.320 --> 14:40.840
See the carvings on this rock?

14:41.680 --> 14:45.440
They show people celebrating,
dancing around a bonfire.

14:46.480 --> 14:48.160
That dancing girl carving

14:49.720 --> 14:52.240
kind of reminds me of my sister.

14:54.560 --> 14:56.360
Lu Wuyi has always loved

14:57.640 --> 14:58.960
to dance too.

15:35.240 --> 15:37.520
That was the chieftain's daughter.

15:37.600 --> 15:39.040
Her name was Di Zhu.

15:39.720 --> 15:41.640
That means "Pearl of the Earth".

15:43.160 --> 15:45.320
The chieftain must have adored her

15:45.920 --> 15:47.600
to give her such a grand name.

15:47.680 --> 15:48.840
Yes.

15:50.240 --> 15:53.240
He adored her so much,
he even decided to give her

15:53.320 --> 15:54.560
the Star Stone as a dowry.

15:55.320 --> 15:58.240
He who carries a treasure
invites hungry eyes.

15:58.840 --> 16:00.320
The chieftain did love his daughter,

16:00.400 --> 16:01.880
but in a foolish way.

16:03.080 --> 16:05.120
Now that the Star Stone
had mysterious power,

16:05.640 --> 16:07.880
it would draw envy

16:07.960 --> 16:09.120
and bring disaster.

16:09.720 --> 16:10.720
What?

16:11.520 --> 16:12.920
You've heard this story too?

16:14.760 --> 16:16.160
Did it really bring disaster?

16:18.440 --> 16:19.360
Yes.

16:19.880 --> 16:22.920
Every man who loved Di Zhu
and asked for her hand

16:23.520 --> 16:25.080
died mysteriously.

16:25.160 --> 16:27.360
Only a young man named Man Man,

16:27.440 --> 16:28.960
who won her love,

16:29.040 --> 16:31.680
remained unharmed, seemed blessed.

16:32.680 --> 16:34.680
If this were any normal legend,

16:36.160 --> 16:37.280
I'd guess

16:38.680 --> 16:41.480
this Man Man was no ordinary man.

16:41.560 --> 16:43.400
He pretended to love her,

16:43.480 --> 16:44.960
but really came for the Star Stone.

16:45.040 --> 16:49.080
All those other suitors
were killed by him too.

16:50.320 --> 16:51.600
Sure enough.

16:53.360 --> 16:56.520
Only a liar knows a liar best.

16:57.440 --> 16:58.440
Thanks.

17:03.200 --> 17:05.680
Actually, that Man Man
was a high-rank Green Ape demon.

17:06.200 --> 17:07.839
He tricked Di Zhu into loving him

17:08.359 --> 17:09.800
to steal the Star Stone.

17:10.400 --> 17:11.880
When his plan fell apart,

17:11.960 --> 17:13.160
he rallied the Green Apes

17:13.240 --> 17:14.800
to take the stone by force

17:15.560 --> 17:17.440
and unleashed a hurricane on the tribe.

17:18.040 --> 17:19.839
Di Zhu died.

17:20.359 --> 17:22.079
The Aodeng tribe was wiped out.

17:22.880 --> 17:24.839
The young man, Man Man,

17:24.920 --> 17:28.240
and the Star Stone
vanished without a trace.

17:29.760 --> 17:31.160
Poor Di Zhu.

17:33.720 --> 17:35.440
What she thought was true love

17:36.280 --> 17:38.960
was nothing but a lie,
a carefully planned one.

17:40.720 --> 17:44.000
Those who trick others' hearts
deserve to die.

17:52.440 --> 17:54.200
Maybe Man Man had his reasons.

17:58.040 --> 17:59.000
What's this?

18:00.400 --> 18:01.760
Sympathizing with a liar?

18:03.520 --> 18:08.440
Master Wu, aren't you a liar yourself?

18:47.440 --> 18:48.400
Wuyi.

18:49.560 --> 18:50.600
Wangyan.

19:16.160 --> 19:17.080
Wangyan!

19:18.080 --> 19:18.920
Lu Wuyi!

20:02.840 --> 20:03.920
Wu Zhiqi.

20:10.040 --> 20:10.960
I've seen him.

20:26.560 --> 20:28.240
Greetings, Master Dragon Deity.

20:30.120 --> 20:31.160
Master,

20:32.720 --> 20:34.680
have you come to judge me?

20:35.960 --> 20:37.160
If you know it's wrong,

20:38.080 --> 20:39.640
why do you persist?

20:46.720 --> 20:49.960
The Six-Eyed Butterfly told me
how to save my people.

20:51.720 --> 20:53.440
He gave me hope.

20:55.680 --> 20:58.000
I'm just one step away.

20:59.040 --> 21:00.240
Over a hundred years,

21:02.440 --> 21:03.680
Wu Zhiqi,

21:04.360 --> 21:06.200
you still haven't let go?

21:07.360 --> 21:08.960
I only ask you

21:10.440 --> 21:12.360
to give me a little more time.

21:14.320 --> 21:16.120
If I can save my people,

21:16.200 --> 21:19.080
then live or die,

21:19.680 --> 21:21.120
I'll accept it.

21:21.200 --> 21:23.240
I can't give you time.

21:23.920 --> 21:26.080
I'm taking my power back right now.

22:34.480 --> 22:35.920
The Twelve Thoughts!

23:20.280 --> 23:22.680
Yuan Wuhuo didn't lie to me.

23:25.280 --> 23:28.240
Sinners' blood can awaken the Star Stone!

23:56.480 --> 23:57.320
Master!

24:35.440 --> 24:36.680
Let go, Master!

25:48.080 --> 25:49.320
No!

27:22.080 --> 27:23.640
-Let's celebrate.
-Come quickly!

27:23.720 --> 27:24.560
Come!

27:29.240 --> 27:30.560
Come!

27:35.600 --> 27:41.000
ONE THOUSAND YEARS AGO, AODENG TRIBE

28:19.680 --> 28:21.720
Look! The chieftain's daughter is here!

28:21.800 --> 28:22.960
The chieftain's daughter is here!

28:30.760 --> 28:36.360
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

28:37.160 --> 28:41.000
-Bravo!
-So beautiful!

28:41.640 --> 28:43.240
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

28:47.800 --> 28:49.200
Beautiful!

28:51.240 --> 28:57.080
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

28:57.160 --> 29:00.160
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

29:02.200 --> 29:06.040
Bravo!

29:07.440 --> 29:12.080
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

29:50.920 --> 29:54.360
ONE HUNDRED FIFTY YEARS AGO
GREEN APE TRIBE

29:54.440 --> 29:55.400
Yuan Xizai?

29:57.680 --> 29:58.680
Yuan Xizai?

30:03.400 --> 30:04.880
YUAN WUHUO

30:04.960 --> 30:06.080
Yuan Xizai!

30:15.320 --> 30:16.160
Who are you?

30:17.080 --> 30:18.160
Who am I?

30:19.200 --> 30:21.280
I'm your brother, Yuan Wuhuo.

30:21.800 --> 30:23.040
Yuan Wuhuo?

30:23.680 --> 30:25.000
The butterfly demon!

30:26.200 --> 30:27.280
Where's my knife?

30:29.720 --> 30:31.320
Did you hit your head?

31:43.680 --> 31:44.640
Wu Zhiqi!

31:45.760 --> 31:47.280
What demon magic did you use?

31:47.360 --> 31:49.440
Release Wu Shiguang and the rest!

31:50.000 --> 31:51.160
You're overconfident.

32:39.360 --> 32:40.400
Bai Ze?

32:46.040 --> 32:49.040
Wu Zhiqi,
you can't take back the Star Stone now.

32:49.120 --> 32:51.440
You're siding against me too?

32:51.520 --> 32:52.760
You betrayed the Dragon Deity.

32:52.840 --> 32:54.400
Of course I'm against you.

32:55.280 --> 32:56.160
But right now,

32:56.680 --> 32:58.480
they're trapped inside the Star Stone.

32:59.080 --> 33:01.720
If you take it back, they'll all die.

33:02.320 --> 33:04.000
You think I care?

33:04.080 --> 33:04.920
You do.

33:05.000 --> 33:06.480
Because if they die,

33:07.440 --> 33:09.320
your wish will never come true.

33:11.720 --> 33:12.720
What do you mean?

33:12.800 --> 33:14.960
I know you want to use
the Star Stone's power

33:15.040 --> 33:16.360
to save your people.

33:16.440 --> 33:19.840
But… you've had this stone for so long.

33:19.920 --> 33:21.360
Are they alive?

33:24.280 --> 33:27.840
The Star Stone needs sinners' blood
to be activated.

33:28.520 --> 33:31.480
So I've been waiting
for Wu Shiguang to come.

33:31.560 --> 33:33.040
Yuan Wuhuo lied to you.

33:33.120 --> 33:35.160
If you truly want to save your people,

33:35.240 --> 33:37.240
wait until they get out safely.

33:37.880 --> 33:38.960
What are you saying?

33:39.600 --> 33:42.920
This Star Stone you have
has already lost all its power.

33:43.000 --> 33:45.160
It's just an ordinary rock now.

33:45.240 --> 33:49.560
The real Star Stone
is hidden inside that Star Stone illusion.

33:50.160 --> 33:52.800
Only when they retrieve
the real one from within

33:52.880 --> 33:56.880
will the one in your hand regain its power

33:56.960 --> 33:58.680
and become the true Star Stone.

33:59.960 --> 34:01.600
Why should I trust you?

34:01.680 --> 34:03.880
Then why did you trust Yuan Wuhuo?

34:06.120 --> 34:06.960
Trust me.

34:07.040 --> 34:10.239
Your people will be saved.

34:13.480 --> 34:14.320
Master Know-It-All,

34:14.400 --> 34:15.719
what's going on now?

34:22.159 --> 34:23.920
Why is there Jiu Ying's demonic energy?

34:34.719 --> 34:36.080
It's Yuan Wuhuo's trick.

34:37.400 --> 34:38.320
So,

34:38.840 --> 34:42.560
he wanted to use the Star Stone
to trap the Dragon Deity inside

34:42.639 --> 34:44.600
and steal his power.

34:44.679 --> 34:46.120
But now, not just the Dragon Deity,

34:46.199 --> 34:48.719
Wu Shiguang, the pretty lady,
the feisty girl,

34:48.800 --> 34:50.520
and that big guy, they're all in there!

34:50.600 --> 34:52.560
It will cost a bunch, Master Bai Ze!

34:56.840 --> 34:58.400
Yuan Wuhuo…

35:00.080 --> 35:01.240
really tricked me.

35:02.200 --> 35:04.280
They must get the Star Stone

35:04.800 --> 35:06.840
from their own time before it shatters,

35:07.600 --> 35:10.080
-or else…
-But this stone's about to break!

35:11.280 --> 35:15.320
I can use the Eastern Purple Lightning
to buy them some time.

35:22.840 --> 35:24.040
Man Man!

35:24.120 --> 35:26.000
-Did I dance well?
-Man Man?

35:26.800 --> 35:28.080
I practiced for so long.

35:28.160 --> 35:29.320
Come on, praise me!

35:30.200 --> 35:31.120
Praise me!

35:31.200 --> 35:32.440
I don't know how to praise.

35:32.520 --> 35:33.560
Just do it!

35:33.640 --> 35:35.560
Say I'm like a butterfly, a peacock.

35:36.160 --> 35:37.920
-Lu…
-As a deer?

35:38.000 --> 35:39.360
A deer in the forest?

35:39.440 --> 35:41.080
You mean I'm light on my feet?

35:41.920 --> 35:43.520
-Hey, what's wrong with you?
-Shut up.

35:43.600 --> 35:45.520
If you don't want to get caught,
dance now.

35:45.600 --> 35:47.600
-Dance!
-I can't dance!

35:48.120 --> 35:49.280
Spin around!

35:50.400 --> 35:51.360
Wave your hands!

35:51.440 --> 35:52.400
Just dance!

35:54.040 --> 35:54.880
Man Man,

35:54.960 --> 35:56.120
you got an itch or what?

35:59.240 --> 36:00.680
What are you looking at?

36:00.760 --> 36:02.080
I just prayed to the Fire Deity

36:02.160 --> 36:04.440
that you'll only look
at me tonight, forever.

36:04.520 --> 36:06.280
Don't push it.

36:24.760 --> 36:26.120
What do you want?

36:26.640 --> 36:28.560
I want a couple's dance with Di Zhu.

36:28.640 --> 36:29.480
A couple's dance

36:29.560 --> 36:31.360
is for lovers seeking blessings.

36:31.440 --> 36:32.720
We're not lovers.

36:32.800 --> 36:33.640
Why would I dance with you?

36:33.720 --> 36:34.720
Da Ji,

36:35.640 --> 36:37.400
the chieftain's away,
but don't start trouble.

36:39.160 --> 36:40.880
Look at that delicate little guy.

36:40.960 --> 36:41.800
A breeze would knock him down.

36:41.880 --> 36:42.760
How is he any better than me?

36:44.560 --> 36:45.760
He's better in any way.

36:45.840 --> 36:47.400
He's proud, yet gentle.

36:47.480 --> 36:50.720
His eyes are fierce like a wolf king's,
yet pure as the moon.

36:50.800 --> 36:52.240
Man Man protects me,

36:52.320 --> 36:54.840
praises me, and holds me in his hands.

36:55.840 --> 36:57.040
Right?

36:58.280 --> 36:59.720
Am I right?

37:00.800 --> 37:01.640
Right.

37:02.920 --> 37:04.160
What's the point of all this?

37:04.240 --> 37:06.120
He's just a poor kid from somewhere else.

37:06.200 --> 37:09.120
Di Zhu, you should be with me.

37:11.320 --> 37:12.360
Kneel!

37:16.120 --> 37:17.200
Kneel?

37:18.680 --> 37:19.760
Too much wine, huh?

37:24.400 --> 37:25.680
What are you doing?

37:25.760 --> 37:26.600
You hit him too hard!

37:26.680 --> 37:28.200
Who's stronger?

37:36.400 --> 37:37.360
Freeze?

37:37.440 --> 37:39.480
-You…
-Enough. Let's go now!

37:40.000 --> 37:41.000
Get out!

37:43.560 --> 37:46.000
Di Zhu, I won't give up on you!

37:46.080 --> 37:47.920
You and the Star Stone are both mine!

37:48.680 --> 37:49.720
Man Man.

37:53.160 --> 37:54.680
Man Man,

37:54.760 --> 37:57.160
I roasted a leg of lamb for you. Try it.

37:58.600 --> 37:59.480
It's really good.

38:00.240 --> 38:02.680
No, thanks. I'm a vegetarian.

38:05.640 --> 38:08.880
Master Chi Wen, are you sulking
because he beat you?

38:09.720 --> 38:11.880
What, a Dragon Deity
who's lived millions of years

38:11.960 --> 38:13.400
could be so childish?

38:14.440 --> 38:16.880
I already got back at him for you.

38:16.960 --> 38:17.920
Still not happy?

38:20.200 --> 38:23.080
If you don't want to be pushed around,

38:23.160 --> 38:24.760
why not use your power?

38:27.360 --> 38:28.200
Because…

38:29.120 --> 38:30.440
I'm Man Man now.

38:31.720 --> 38:34.320
Man Man and Wu Zhiqi
are both Green Ape demons.

38:34.400 --> 38:36.000
They can control the wind and sand.

38:37.000 --> 38:37.920
Can you?

38:49.720 --> 38:50.560
I can't.

38:51.440 --> 38:52.880
My power is sealed.

38:53.720 --> 38:54.560
Why?

38:55.240 --> 38:56.360
Maybe…

38:57.800 --> 38:59.520
Man Man doesn't want to reveal himself.

39:00.760 --> 39:05.200
So now you're a mere mortal
with none of your old might,

39:06.000 --> 39:10.160
a totally helpless dragon
at my mercy, huh?

39:11.600 --> 39:13.280
Di Zhu is a mortal too.

39:14.360 --> 39:17.720
How come you can still use
Formless Moon magic?

39:19.360 --> 39:20.720
I don't know.

39:22.480 --> 39:24.800
Maybe the Formless Moon
is stronger than your Shilin Sect.

39:37.000 --> 39:39.600
The nine spots on your head are pretty.

39:41.960 --> 39:43.200
Let me call you

39:44.240 --> 39:45.360
Little Nine.

39:45.440 --> 39:47.160
Aren't you scared of it at all?

39:53.560 --> 39:56.960
Without Wangyan here,
I am a little scared.

39:57.480 --> 39:58.880
But

39:59.400 --> 40:01.400
I feel like she's nearby.

40:01.920 --> 40:03.320
You know why that is?

40:03.920 --> 40:04.720
I do.

40:05.920 --> 40:08.920
Because this is the past illusion
inside the Star Stone.

40:10.120 --> 40:11.400
Your sister

40:12.440 --> 40:13.640
is probably in another illusion.

41:09.240 --> 41:14.480
ONE HUNDRED YEARS AGO, FLOOD DRAGON TRIBE
